<br>
As for the class balancing, the only answer I received is that Wizards (as well as other classes) were not &quot;finished&quot; in the realm of updates.  I am aware that this is a very WIDE open statement, but the glimmer of hope remains.  Maybe the board is closed, but the development is not.  Unless we've been yet again boldfacely lied to.  Wouldn't be surprised.<br>
<br>
If anything, the statement that bothered me more than any other was the one saying that Wizards truly got a nice kick upstairs with the two level 60 spells.  You could not make me more angry to say that wizards are truly the only class that has nothing to look forward to BEFORE level 60.  Melee armor, stronger Necro and mage pets, Major Heals, etc.   They all are obtainable before 60.  We on the other hand, well, I don't think I need to expand upon it.<br>
<br>
Overall, having listened to questions at both Baltimore and San Diego, have come to the conclusion that these people are EXPERTS in the ability to give NON-answers.  Maybe they should be running our country.<br>
<br>
And two the young lady who said they wouldn't be supporting another Verant game in the future because their customer service boarders on pariah status...   CHEERS TO YOU!!!!!  Finally, someone had the nerve to speak out in public, and the crowd at the Fan Faire went WILD for her.  Nice job! <!--EZCODE EMOTICON START :) --><img src=http://www.ezboard.com/intl/aenglish/images/emoticons/smile.gif ALT=":)"><!--EZCODE EMOTICON END--> <br>
<br>
W.F. <p></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#33333><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub23.ezboard.com/uaendayar.showPublicProfile?language=EN>Aendayar</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Forum Wizard</span><br>  Posts: 135<br> <font color=#ffffff>(4/10/01 9:32 am)</font><br>    </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> Re: Another Fan Faire Report...</span><hr size=1> I don't think they'll be adding any time of manaregain because enchanters would complain too much.  I'm holding out for either an upgrade to concussion or a nice new magic based lure. <p></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#000000><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub23.ezboard.com/uakkronn.showPublicProfile?language=EN>Akkronn</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Forum Apprentice</span><br>  Posts: 8<br> <font color=#ffffff>(4/10/01 11:04 am)</font><br>    </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> Yooohoo the hope reborn</span><hr size=1>    Thank to all guys who going to fair fan(lucky guys <!--EZCODE EMOTICON START :) --><img src=http://www.ezboard.com/intl/aenglish/images/emoticons/smile.gif ALT=":)"><!--EZCODE EMOTICON END--> ) and come back whit a little bit of hope.<br>
